netcdf plugin for OpenCPN 4.2.0
==============================

Compiling 
=========
The plugin can be built standalone.
* clone the plugin repository from github

Place opencpn.lib in your build directory.

Build as normally:

Used CMake.gui

Only tested with Windows/VS 2013.

Install NetCDF 4.4.0 from the extras folder. Link to netcdf.lib etc etc.

IMPORTANT: Only coded for OpenGL OFF

